#. module: it_hardware
#: model:product.template,description_sale:it_hardware.product_template_7
msgid ""
"A 35.5cms (14) 2-in-1 touchscreen laptop, the ThinkPad X1 Yoga Gen 7 delivers features that matter.\n"
"        Enjoy the spectacular Communications Bar that raises the bar on collaboration.\n"
"        Robust security includes Tile® tracking technology—just in case.\n"
"        Plus, high-performance 12th Gen Intel® Core™ vPro processing, on the Intel® Evo™ platform provides super-responsive, on-the-go power."
msgstr ""
"ແລັບທັອບໜ້າຈໍສຳຜັດແບບ 2-in-1 ຂະໜາດ 35.5 ຊມ (14 ນິ້ວ), ThinkPad X1 Yoga Gen 7 ມາພ້ອມຄຸນ"
"ສົມບັດທີ່ສຳຄັນ.\n"
"        ເພີດເພີນໄປກັບ Communications Bar ທີ່ຊ່ວຍຍົກລະດັບການເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັນ.\n"
"        ຄວາມປອດໄພທີ່ແຂງແກ່ນ ລວມທັງເຕັກໂນໂລຊີການຕິດຕາມ Tile®.\n"
"        ພ້ອມດ້ວຍໜ່ວຍປະມວນຜົນ Intel® Core™ vPro ເຈັນເນີເຣຊັນທີ 12 ທີ່ມີປະສິດທິພາບສູງ ບົນແພລັດຟ"
"ອມ Intel® Evo™ ທີ່ໃຫ້ພະລັງການເຮັດວຽກທີ່ວ່ອງໄວໃນທຸກບ່ອນ."

#. module: it_hardware
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:it_hardware.homepage
